item.title: My SOTW (please CnC)
item.dc:creator: @ThAt0n36Uy Elijah
item.description:
@ThAt0n36Uy wrote:

There’s no focal point, you just have an image inserted in there. it’s like a grungy mess. you need to make the image the focal point of the image, and use brushes blend, and make the image more appealing. not just blur the shit out of everything. The text shouldn’t be the most noticeable thing, unless you feel it should be. Make the text flip of the end of the Stock image, or make it blend with the rest.

I give it a 3.7/10, read some tutorials on abstract and text effects.
